{"tid":1677262,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"IU 巡演《Love, Poem》門票開賣　台北場兩分鐘售空！","createTime":"2019-10-27T03:58:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-27T17:17:49.000Z","uid":34643,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"b013848079e27993c5df0f291c5b66c809879a40","tid":1677262,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T03:58:38.000Z","msg":"IU 的年底巡演即將開跑，首場門票毫不意外地火速售罄，希望 Uaena 們都能順利買到其他場次的票<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.tickettw.com/images/posters/1273.jpg?v=89199\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.tickettw.com%2Fimages%2Fposters%2F1273.jpg%3Fv%3D89199&h=f2cad066&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nIU 剛剛經由 TixCraft 開賣了亞洲巡迴演唱會《Love, Poem》的台北場門票，結果在短短兩分鐘內就被搶購一空，再度印證了票房威力。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/a/2019-10-08/120825-777985.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fa%2F2019-10-08%2F120825-777985.jpg&h=7b04f2a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n以 11 月 2 日的光州場為起點，IU 的《Love, Poem》也將陸續前往仁川 (11/09)、釜山 (11/16) 和首爾 (11/23~11/24) 舉行。<br />\n<br />\n進入 12 月後，IU 就會來到台灣開啟海外場次，目前在 12 月 28 日前已敲定的場次依序有新加坡、菲律賓、馬來西亞、泰國和印尼，最近一定要記得關注售票資訊哦！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/a/2019-10-08/120825-777986.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fa%2F2019-10-08%2F120825-777986.jpg&h=f58bf541&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://data.whicdn.com/images/332507696/original.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdata.whicdn.com%2Fimages%2F332507696%2Foriginal.jpg&h=a6fb070e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a314a40e48a66283ccc9b261b4830d83665916ff","tid":1677262,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T03:58:46.000Z","msg":"【黃色經濟】有個傻仔整咗個黃藍商鋪認證平台<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eqgeNS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eqgeNS</a><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3131839f0e63edbae1d38560fffd0610b86fd3d",